{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197640/extras/aboutPageGif1.gif?t=1739526563\" /><br><br>Nix's life changed forever when the biggest corporation on earth known as <i>Nascent</i> kidnapped his girlfriend. He doesn't know why or who exactly did it, but he decides to construct a <i>RoboSuit</i> and go on a mission to fight his way through anything he has to. <i>Will he be able to get her back?</i><br><br>Explore the Nascent's child-corporation buildings to find the secret to getting your girlfriend back. Gather as much intel as possible and destroy the evil plan of Nascent as it sends more and more security bots to stop you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197640/extras/aboutPageGif2.gif?t=1739526563\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li><strong>Momentum-based movement system</strong> - That includes sliding, double jumping and lots of high-speed actions!<br>    </li><li><strong>High-octane melee combat system</strong> - Allows the player to switch between 4 Suit Combat Modes (Stances) that change the way the Main Character interacts with enemies and what combos they perform.<br>    </li><li><strong>Style Rating System</strong> - A meter that keeps track of how stylish player's performance is.<br>    </li><li><strong>Old superhero comic aesthetic</strong> - Hand crafted textures for characters with outlines and vibrant colors to get that old superhero suit look.<br>    </li><li><strong>Many Abilities</strong> - Additional combat features that get unlocked as the player progresses that can be chained with regular combos to inflict the most amount of damage.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197640/extras/aboutPageGif3.gif?t=1739526563\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite